  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK290">
<l>kaḷvārkkut taḷḷu muyirnilai kaḷḷārkkut</l>
<l>taḷḷātu puttē ḷulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even their body will fail the fraudulent but even the world of the gods will not fail those who are free from fraud.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
